EVNE Developers – is a progressive and dynamic IT service company that has creatively operated within the international market of Web & Mobile development since 2011. 
The Research & Development Center of the company is situated in the central region of Ukraine, which also has branches in Germany and in the USA as well. 
Throughout history, EVNE Developers has cooperated with more than 170 partners from more than 18 countries, and more than 650 projects in a variety of fields have been created by our experts. 
We focus on:
    •    eCommerce and eLearning;
    •    Corporate portals and reservation services;
    •    High-load web and mobile applications’ development;
    •    Gaming and Software development;
    •    UI/Ux and graphic design.
Our skill set includes 6 programming languages and a variety of their frameworks, more than 10 Content Management Systems and variety of other technologies.
Excellence Highlights:
    •    EVNE Developers is a top-rate agency at Upwork with 14K+ hours worked,  100% job success rating and 5 star client feedback;
    •    A five-pointer mark from all clients at Clutch.co;
    •    More than 20 certificates of appreciation, and
    •    40% of returning customers.
